Darker Grotesque Light Regular (DarkerGrotesque-Light.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'DarkerGrotesque-Light', Everything looks good.

Pass

Darker Grotesque Light Regular (DarkerGrotesque-Light.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Darker Grotesque' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Light' = NID 1 'Darker Grotesque Light'.

Darker Grotesque Regular (DarkerGrotesque-Regular.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'DarkerGrotesque-Regular', Everything looks good.

Darker Grotesque Medium Regular (DarkerGrotesque-Medium.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'DarkerGrotesque-Medium', Everything looks good.

Pass

, most common Monotype license test is:
This font software is the property of Monotype Imaging Inc., or one of its affiliated entities (collectively, Monotype) and its use by you is covered under the terms of a license agreement. You have obtained this font software either directly from Monotype or together with software distributed by one of the licensees of Monotype. This software is a valuable asset of Monotype. Unless you have entered into a specific license agreement granting you additional rights, your use of this software is limited by the terms of the actual license agreement you have entered into with Monotype. You may not copy or distribute this software. If you have any questions concerning your rights you should review the license agreement you received with the software. You can learn more about Monotype by clicking here: www.monotype.com.

Darker Grotesque Medium Regular (DarkerGrotesque-Medium.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Darker Grotesque' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Medium' = NID 1 'Darker Grotesque Medium'.

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Darker Grotesque' + 'Space' + NID 17 'SemiBold' = NID 1 'Darker Grotesque SemiBold'.

Darker Grotesque Bold (DarkerGrotesque-Bold.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.

NID 6 is 'DarkerGrotesque-Bold', Everything looks good.

Darker Grotesque ExtraBold Regular (DarkerGrotesque-ExtraBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'DarkerGrotesque-ExtraBold', Everything looks good.

Darker Grotesque ExtraBold Regular (DarkerGrotesque-ExtraBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Darker Grotesque' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraBold' = NID 1 'Darker Grotesque ExtraBold'.

Darker Grotesque Black Regular (DarkerGrotesque-Black.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'DarkerGrotesque-Black', Everything looks good.

Pass

Unless you have entered into a specific license agreement granting you additional rights, your use of this software is limited by the terms of the actual license agreement you have entered into with Monotype. You may not copy or distribute this software. If you have any questions concerning your rights you should review the license agreement you received with the software. Darker Grotesque Black Regular (DarkerGrotesque-Black.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Darker Grotesque' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Black' = NID 1 'Darker Grotesque Black'.
